[[sn:May 29 (Old Lunar Calendar)]] [[cdo:5 nguŏk 29 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[ja:5月29日 (旧暦)]] [[ko:음력 5월 29일]] [[zh_min_nan:5 goe̍h 29 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh_yue:五月廿九]] [[zh:五月廿九]] [[en:draft:May 29 (Old Lunar Calendar)]]{{Lunar May}} {{Lunar May}} '''May 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|May (Old Lunar Calendar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Old Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Old Lunar Calendar}}. If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小}} then this is the last day of the month. Otherwise if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大}} then it is the second last day.{{citation needed|replace this with source on all articles}} It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負}}.
