* {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1819]] {{ill|July 20|ja|7月20日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saion|ja|徳川斉温|qq=|12=draft}}, the 11th daimyō of the Owari Domain (died [[1839]]).
