* {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Soga Jigorō Tokuchi|ja|曾我五郎時致|qq=|12=draft}}, a samurai and the younger brother of Soga (born [[1174]]).
