== Deaths == * {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Soga Jigorō Tokuchi|ja|曾我五郎時致|qq=|qq=draft}}, a samurai and the younger brother of Soga (born [[1174]]). * [[Tenmei]] 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1788]] {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Goryōken Kayū|ja|呉陵軒可有|qq=|qq=draft}}, a miscellaneous haiku writer known as "Yanudaru" (柳多留). * [[Bunka]] 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1817]] {{ill|July 13|ja|7月13日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kaiho Seiryō|ja|海保青陵|qq=|qq=draft}}, a Confucian scholar and economic reformer (born [[1755]]).
