== Births == * [[Ōei]] 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1404]] {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 6|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yamana Sōzen|ja|山名宗全|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamana Sōzen|qq=}} (also known as Mochiyutaka), a military commander (died [[1473]])<ref>{{Harvnb|百目木|1918|p=2|qq=}}</ref>. * [[Eishō]] 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1517]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 18|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shin-chikamachi Tennō|ja|正親町天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shin-chikamachi Tennō|qq=}}, the 106th Emperor of Japan (died [[1593]]). * [[Genna]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1618]] {{ill|July 21|ja|7月21日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 21|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hayashi Ga-hō|ja|林鵞峰|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hayashi Ga-hō|qq=}} (also known as Shunsai), a Confucian scholar and the son of Hayashi Razan (died [[1680]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1819]] {{ill|July 20|ja|7月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 20|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saion|ja|徳川斉温|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Saion|qq=}}, the 11th daimyō of the Owari Domain (died [[1839]]). * Bunkyū 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1862, June 26) – {{ill|Minasaku Motohachi|ja|箕作元八|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minasaku Motohachi|qq=}}, a historian and the fourth son of Minasaku Akutsubo (died [[1919]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kenkyū|ja|建久|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenkyū|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1193]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Soga Jigorō Tokuchi|ja|曾我五郎時致|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Jigorō Tokuchi|qq=}}, a samurai and the younger brother of Soga (born [[1174]]). * [[Tenmei]] 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1788]] {{ill|July 2|ja|7月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Goryōken Kayū|ja|呉陵軒可有|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Goryōken Kayū|qq=}}, a miscellaneous haiku writer known as "Yanudaru" (柳多留). * [[Bunka]] 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1817]] {{ill|July 13|ja|7月13日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 13|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kaiho Seiryō|ja|海保青陵|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaiho Seiryō|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar and economic reformer (born [[1755]]).
