== Deaths == * [[:en:Kenkyū|Kenkyū]] 4th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1193]] [[:en:June 29|June 29]]) – {{ill|Soga Jigorō Tokuchi|ja|曾我五郎時致|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Jigorō Tokuchi|qq=}}, a samurai and the younger brother of Soga (born [[1174]]). * [[Tenmei]] 8th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1788]] [[:en:July 2|July 2]]) – {{ill|Goryōken Kayū|ja|呉陵軒可有|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Goryōken Kayū|qq=}}, a miscellaneous haiku writer known as "Yanudaru" (柳多留). * [[Bunka]] 14th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1817]] [[:en:July 13|July 13]]) – {{ill|Kaiho Seiryō|ja|海保青陵|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaiho Seiryō|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar and economic reformer (born [[1755]]).
